			<Text>Happiness is really a luxury to your people.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_KOKORO_INSULT_CITIES_1">
			<Text>You have even nowhere to lead off emotions.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_KOKORO_INSULT_POPULATION_1">
			<Text>Living as a puppet can be boring, but you seem enjoy it.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_KOKORO_INSULT_CULTURE_1">
			<Text>If you are a student of Keine, she will soon go mad.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_KOKORO_INSULT_CULTURE_2">
			<Text>Don't worry, you won't be the one interviewed by Himekaidou Hatate.</Text>
		</Row>

		<!-- ==================================== Trade ==================================== -->
		<!-- AI is offering a trade because they want a luxury from you -->
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_KOKORO_LUXURY_TRADE_1">
			<Text>I wish to taste your snack, of course I'll pay it.</Text>
		</Row>
		<!-- AI is asking for a mutual open borders agreement -->
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_KOKORO_OPEN_BORDERS_EXCHANGE_1">
			<Text>Opening borders helps us exchange our minds.</Text>
		</Row>

		<!-- ==================================== Player declares war on the AI ==================================== -->
		<!-- AI Attacked by another player -->
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_KOKORO_ATTACKED_HOSTILE_1">
			<Text>I will use your desperation make a new mask.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_KOKORO_ATTACKED_HOSTILE_2">
			<Text>So you are better than the combination of Reimu, Byakuren and Miko?</Text>
		</Row>
	

		<!-- ==================================== AI declares war on the player ==================================== -->
		<!-- Generic response -->
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_KOKORO_DOW_GENERIC_1">
			<Text>In the name of strongest, let's fight it out.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_KOKORO_DOW_GENERIC_2">
			<Text>Time to recycle hope!</Text>
		</Row>

		<!-- AI is in a land dispute with the player -->
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_KOKORO_DOW_LAND_1">
			<Text>If you wish to approach and tribute your hope, I agree.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_KOKORO_DOW_LAND_2">
			<Text>I have no choice, remember you made it.</Text>
		</Row>
		<!-- AI declares war after the player refuses a demand -->
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_KOKORO_WAR_DEMAND_REFUSED_1">
			<Text>This being so, I need to change my mask.</Text>
		</Row>

		<!-- ==================================== Peace offers ==================================== -->

		<!-- AI doesn't want to have peace -->
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_KOKORO_NO_PEACE_1">
			<Text>The "strongest" hasn't been decided.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_KOKORO_NO_PEACE_2">
			<Text>Never. I haven't collected enough hope.</Text>
		</Row>
		<!-- Player asks for peace on the same turn war was declared - no peace! -->
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_KOKORO_TOO_SOON_NO_PEACE_1">
			<Text>This is a true war, not play.</Text>
		</Row>

		<!-- ==================================== Cultural Influence ==================================== -->
		<!-- Player is influential on the AI (Our people are wearing your blue jeans...) -->
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_KOKORO_INFLUENTIAL_ON_AI_1">
			<Text>I have to tell that, my masks have been poured with your emotions.</Text>
		</Row>
		<!-- AI is influential on the player -->
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_KOKORO_INFLUENTIAL_ON_HUMAN_1">
			<Text>Now you and your people can feel my emotions, right?</Text>
		</Row>
